ploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n"},{"title":"hi","date":"2023-04-15T19:00:11.000Z","_content":"hi","source":"_posts/hi.md","raw":"---\ntitle: hi\ndate: 2023-04-16 03:00:11\ntags:\n---\nhi","slug":"hi","published":1,"updated":"2023-04-15T19:01:22.955Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","_id":"clgitlyrw0000fwts30tm0kxn","content":"<p>hi</p>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<p>hi</p>\n"},{"title":"毕设","date":"2023-04-24T09:16:21.000Z","_content":"\nQ-learning之前的关于强化学习的一些前置知识\n\n**状态** state\n\n**状态空间** state space\n\n**动作** action\n\n**动作空间** action space\n\n**智能体** agent\n\n**环境** environment\n\n**策略** policy\n\n**奖励** reward\n\n**状态转移** state transition\n\n**回报** 奖励的和(加权和，如果有折扣率的话），注意和奖励的区别，强化学习的目的是最大话回报而不是最大化奖励\n\n**马尔可夫过程** 老朋友了，信息论啥的一直会碰见。\n\n\n\n ","source":"_posts/毕设.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 毕设\ndate: 2023-04-24 17:16:21\ntags: 一些知识点\n\n---\n\nQ-learning之前的关于强化学习的一些前置知识\n\n**状态** state\n\n**状态空间** state space\n\n**动作** action\n\n**动作空间** action space\n\n**智能体** agent\n\n**环境** environment\n\n**策略** policy\n\n**奖励** reward\n\n**状态转移** state transition\n\n**回报** 奖励的和(加权和，如果有折扣率的话），注意和奖励的区别，强化学习的目的是最大话回报而不是最大化奖励\n\n**马尔可夫过程** 老朋友了，信息论啥的一直会碰见。\n\n\n\n ","slug":"毕设","published":1,"updated":"2023-04-24T09:38:50.005Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","_id":"clgunc1qg0000r0ts7jg8gwrt","content":"<p>Q-learning之前的关于强化学习的一些前置知识</p>\n<p><strong>状态</strong> state</p>\n<p><strong>状态空间</strong> state space</p>\n<p><strong>动作</strong> action</p>\n<p><strong>动作空间</strong> action space</p>\n<p><strong>智能体</strong> agent</p>\n<p><strong>环境</strong> environment</p>\n<p><strong>策略</strong> policy</p>\n<p><strong>奖励</strong> reward</p>\n<p><strong>状态转移</strong> state transition</p>\n<p><strong>回报</strong> 奖励的和(加权和，如果有折扣率的话），注意和奖励的区别，强化学习的目的是最大话回报而不是最大化奖励</p>\n<p><strong>马尔可夫过程</strong> 老朋友了，信息论啥的一直会碰见。</p>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<p>Q-learning之前的关于强化学习的一些前置知识</p>\n<p><strong>状态</strong> state</p>\n<p><strong>状态空间</strong> state space</p>\n<p><strong>动作</strong> action</p>\n<p><strong>动作空间</strong> action space</p>\n<p><strong>智能体</strong> agent</p>\n<p><strong>环境</strong> environment</p>\n<p><strong>策略</strong> policy</p>\n<p><strong>奖励</strong> reward</p>\n<p><strong>状态转移</strong> state transition</p>\n<p><strong>回报</strong> 奖励的和(加权和，如果有折扣率的话），注意和奖励的区别，强化学习的目的是最大话回报而不是最大化奖励</p>\n<p><strong>马尔可夫过程</strong> 老朋友了，信息论啥的一直会碰见。</p>\n"}],"PostAsset":[],"PostCategory":[],"PostTag":[{"post_id":"clgunc1qg0000r0ts7jg8gwrt","tag_id":"clgunc1qk0001r0ts33azfxty","_id":"clgunc1qm0002r0tsb16eg2dp"}],"Tag":[{"name":"一些知识点","_id":"clgunc1qk0001r0ts33azfxty"}]}}